<title>ạ̉nạ knt bʿyd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̉nạ knt bʿyd kẖạṭy yswʿ lạqạny ḥrrny
 mn ywmhạ bqyt wạḥd tạny yswʿ bḥbh gẖyrny
 1- ạ̉nạ knt fy nẓr nfsy wḥty̱ ạlnạs mn ḥwạly
 ạ̹nsạn kẖạṭy ḥqyr wdẖlyl gẖrqạn fy ạlkẖṭyẗ
 lkn fy ʿynyh klạm tạny wfy qlbh mḥbẗ ḥqyqyẗ
 byqwly ạ̹nt gẖạly wmḥbwb wạ̹ydyh mmdwdẗ lạ̹ydy
 2- ạ̉nạ knt fạkr ạ̹ny msẖ mmkn ywm rạḥ ạ̉tgẖyr
 yswʿ ʿạrf yswʿ qạdr ysẖyl wlạ yʿyr
 wyḥwl ḍʿfy llnṣrẗ wqwẗ jdydẗ fy ḥyạty
 wkl ywm ạ̉ʿysẖ lyswʿ bṭwl ạlʿmr lmmạty
 3- wạlqlb kạn bytmny̱ ḥbyb dạymạaⁿ byqblny
 wlmạ ạlṭyn ygẖrqny yyjy hw ysẖmlny
 lkn mạlqtsẖ zy yswʿ bysẖfy ạlqlb mn dẖnbh
 wlmạ ạ̉kwn fy ḍyq ạ̉w jwʿ yswʿ bykfy mn ḥbh</lyrics>
</song>